      <h1>SV Group: Bringing IT, Operations, and Hospitality Together</h1>
      <p class="lead">Filmed inside a fully operational restaurant serving 350+ guests, Viven captured the synergy between SV Group's IT innovation and its passion for hospitality — a film that now drives recruiting and client engagement.</p>
