    <div>
      <div class="cs-stats"><div class="cs-stat"><div class="v">350+</div><div class="l">guests served during the live shoot</div></div><div class="cs-stat"><div class="v">1 film</div><div class="l">recruiting, sales & brand in one</div></div><div class="cs-stat"><div class="v">“Goosebumps”</div><div class="l">the client’s own words</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<section class="sec" style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cs-article post-body reveal">
      <h2>Client overview: SV Group</h2>
      <p><strong>Industry:</strong> Hospitality and gastronomy.<br><strong>Objective:</strong> Showcase the dynamic interaction between IT and operations while highlighting their core competence — providing exceptional hospitality and culinary experiences.</p>
      <p>To achieve this, SV Group partnered with Viven AG to produce a video that reflects their daily operations and the emotional core of their business.</p>

      <h2>The challenge</h2>
      <p>SV Group faced the challenge of capturing the complexity of their operations — balancing IT innovation with their passion for hospitality and gastronomy. They needed a partner who could authentically represent this synergy, even under the demanding circumstances of a fully operational kitchen.</p>

      <h2>The solution</h2>
      <p>Viven AG worked closely with SV Group to produce a video that exceeded all expectations. From understanding the brief to navigating the bustling environment of a restaurant kitchen, Viven delivered a product that captured both the technical and emotional aspects of SV Group's daily life.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Storytelling:</strong> Highlighted the interplay between IT and operations while emphasising the heart of the business — being exceptional hosts and chefs.</li>
        <li><strong>Adaptability:</strong> Filmed in a live restaurant serving over 350 people, with seamless adjustments to ensure smooth collaboration.</li>
        <li><strong>Engagement:</strong> Maintained open communication, consistently involving SV Group in the creative process so every shot aligned with their vision.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The results</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Recruitment tool:</strong> Showcases the vibrant, dynamic environment to attract top talent and gives candidates a clear sense of what it's like to work for SV Group.</li>
        <li><strong>Customer engagement:</strong> Offers clients a behind-the-scenes look at operations, building trust and confidence in SV Group's competence.</li>
        <li><strong>Emotional connection:</strong> Evokes strong emotions and authentically represents SV Group's everyday life, creating a lasting impression.</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote><p>“Watching the video gives me goosebumps. It's emotional, sometimes hectic, and shows exactly what SV is all about. Viven did a great job capturing how our everyday life works.”</p><cite>— Manuel Wild, SV Group</cite></blockquote>

      <h2>Why Viven AG?</h2>
      <p>Both Manuel Wild and Björn Maciejok from SV Group emphasised Viven AG's professionalism and adaptability throughout the process:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Attention to detail:</strong> “Viven understood exactly what we wanted and even implemented things that weren't on paper to our complete satisfaction.”</li>
        <li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> “They adapted quickly to the challenges of filming in a busy kitchen and always included us in the process.”</li>
        <li><strong>Professionalism:</strong> “The entire production was very communicative and professional, which is crucial when making decisions.”</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>A partnership for the future</h2>
      <p>The final video not only exceeded SV Group's expectations but also serves as a versatile tool for recruitment and client engagement.</p>
      <blockquote><p>“The film helps us recruit, engage customers, and showcase our strengths as a dynamic and competent partner. It exceeded our expectations, and we look forward to collaborating again.”</p><cite>— Manuel Wild &amp; Björn Maciejok, SV Group</cite></blockquote>

      <h2>About SV Group</h2>
      <p>SV Group is a leading hospitality and gastronomy company, known for combining operational excellence with cutting-edge IT solutions. Creating exceptional experiences for guests is at the heart of their success.</p>

      <h2>On set</h2>
      <div class="cs-gallery"><img src="/projects/sv-group-innovation-film-brand-video/01-Inovation_film_VIVEN_Video_Agentur_018.jpg" alt="Behind the scenes — SV Group innovation film by Viven" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /><img src="/projects/sv-group-innovation-film-brand-video/03-Inovation_film_VIVEN_Video_Agentur_002.jpg" alt="Behind the scenes — SV Group innovation film by Viven" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /><img src="/projects/sv-group-innovation-film-brand-video/05-Inovation_film_VIVEN_Video_Agentur_017.jpg" alt="Behind the scenes — SV Group innovation film by Viven" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /><img src="/projects/sv-group-innovation-film-brand-video/08-Inovation_film_VIVEN_Video_Agentur_004.jpg" alt="Behind the scenes — SV Group innovation film by Viven" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <div class="faq">
        <details class="reveal"><summary>Can you film in a live, working environment like a restaurant?</summary><p>Yes — the SV Group film was shot in a restaurant serving over 350 people, with the crew adapting around live service. Careful pre-production makes filming possible without disrupting operations.</p></details>
        <details class="reveal"><summary>What is a corporate video like this used for?</summary><p>SV Group uses the film for recruiting (showing candidates the real working environment), customer engagement (a behind-the-scenes look that builds trust) and brand storytelling — three jobs in one production.</p></details>
        <details class="reveal"><summary>How does Viven keep the client involved during production?</summary><p>Open communication at every step: SV Group was consistently involved in the creative process so every shot aligned with their vision — one reason the result 'exceeded expectations'.</p></details>
        <details class="reveal"><summary>How much does a corporate video cost in Switzerland?</summary><p>Depends on filming days and deliverables. Viven offers clear packages — request a quote and you'll get three concept ideas, timing and a fixed offer within 48 hours, free and without obligation.</p></details>
      </div>

      <p>Explore our <a href={p("services/corporate-video")}>corporate video production</a> or see <a href={p("projects")}>more of our work</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

